text: No Password Necessary () is a 1967 Soviet action movie directed by Boris Grigorev.Человек на своем местеПАРОЛЬ НЕ НУЖЕН (1967) It stars Nikolay Gubenko, Mikhail Fyodorov, and Rodion Nahapetov. == Actors == * Nikolay Gubenko as Commander Blyukher * Mikhail Fyodorov as Pavel Postyshev * Rodion Nahapetov as Vsevolod Vladimirov * Vasiliy Lanovoy * Anastasiya Voznesenskaya as Sashenyka Gavrilina == References == ==Other websites== * Category:Soviet movies Category:1967 movies Category:Soviet action movies
